.SH BUGS
Currently does not support:
- Command chaining (e.g., using `&&`, `||`)
- Advanced shell features (like redirections or pipes)


.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sh (1),
.BR bash (1),
.BR execve (2),
.BR fork (2),
.BR wait (2),
.BR getenv (3)

